and sincerity ♪

287
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,690
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

288
00:15:50,150 --> 00:15:51,450
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

289
00:15:51,770 --> 00:15:53,620
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

290
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:57,030
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

291
00:15:57,250 --> 00:15:58,910
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

292
00:15:59,810 --> 00:16:01,590
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

293
00:16:01,800 --> 00:16:03,490
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

294
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:06,470
♪ Love really hurts ♪

295
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:06,200
