296
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:08,400
Couldn't you ask someone else for help?

297
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:12,360
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

298
00:16:08,700 --> 00:16:10,760
Can you take better care of yourself?

299
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,130
Is that what you wanted to say to me?

300
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:15,560
You...

301
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,680
My business is none of your concern!

302
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:19,150
It's raining!

303
00:16:19,480 --> 00:16:22,140
You'll get sick if you
stay in the rain like this!

304
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,970
♪ Like a moth drawn to the flame ♪

305
00:16:27,300 --> 00:16:30,660
♪ Wandering aimlessly
through the night sky ♪

306
00:16:32,290 --> 00:16:33,910
♪ Until I met you ♪

307
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:38,090
♪ Like fire that finally took my life ♪

308
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:40,480
♪ I thought my deep devotion
and sincerity ♪

309
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:42,610
♪ Would earn your eternal loyalty ♪

310
00:16:42,990 --> 00:16:44,250
♪ Because you are like a cloud ♪

311
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,410
♪ I became a wisp of wind ♪

312
00:16:46,780 --> 00:16:49,800
♪ In the end, all the promises we made ♪

313
00:16:50,130 --> 00:16:51,650
♪ Turned into nothing but emptiness ♪

314
