♪ Once, for your dream ♪

315
00:16:54,610 --> 00:16:56,340
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

316
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:59,330
♪ Love really hurts ♪

317
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:05,030
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

318
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:11,240
♪ Only when you've been hurt by love
do you realize how crazy you once were ♪

319
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:14,660
♪ A beautiful dream
turns into a nightmare in an instant ♪

320
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:20,800
♪ You are a neon light
I could never catch ♪

321
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:23,690
♪ I loved you recklessly ♪

322
00:17:25,069 --> 00:17:27,440
♪ And ended up covered in wounds ♪

323
00:17:28,510 --> 00:17:29,800
♪ Yet I still believe in ♪

324
00:17:30,810 --> 00:17:33,360
♪ The sky after the rain ♪

325
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:36,960
♪ Once, for your dream ♪

326
00:17:37,600 --> 00:17:39,110
♪ I gritted my teeth
and pushed myself forward ♪

327
00:17:40,090 --> 00:17:41,760
♪ Love really hurts ♪

328
00:17:43,300 --> 00:17:47,680
♪ I never thought I could be so brave ♪

329
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:48,600
You're awake.

330
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:58,480
♪ In the end, everything came to nothing ♪

331
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:53,520
Miyu.

332
00:17:53,930 --> 00:17:54,970
Qiaoqi?

333
00:17:56,470 --> 00:17:57,430
Why are you here?

334
00:17:57,450 --> 00:17:59,840
You ask me? I wanted to ask you.

335
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:00,750
How did you get

336
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,650
acute pneumonia just from working?

337
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:03,960
If Mr. Ji hadn't called me,

338
00:18:03,960 --> 00:18:06,560
I wouldn't have known
you were in the hospital.

339
00:18:06,930 --> 00:18:08,030
The hearing aid.

340
00:18:08,380 --> 00:18:09,820
Lie down. Don't move.

341
00:18:11,300 --> 00:18:12,760
I knew you'd ask this.

342
00:18:12,890 --> 00:18:14,350
Mr. Ji already had someone

343
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:17,000
send the hearing aid back to the hotel
for the student last night.

344
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,330
He told you not to worry.

345
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:22,750
What about him?

346
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:26,480
He said there was something going on
at the hotel, so he went back.

347
00:18:28,270 --> 00:18:29,870
What's going on with you two?

348
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:31,110
Did you fight?

349
00:18:32,200 --> 00:18:34,200
He looked pretty worried about you.

350
00:18:35,550 --> 00:18:37,280
Don't bother with him anymore.

351
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,040
Get some rest.

352
00:18:53,130 --> 00:18:53,650
Come in.

353
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:56,400
Mr. Xue,

354
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:57,830
Mr. Qian from the sales department

355
00:18:57,830 --> 00:18:59,900
and Mr. Huang from the finance department
keep asking

356
00:18:59,900 --> 00:19:02,030
if the project progress report meeting
later is still on.

357
00:19:02,030 --> 00:19:03,550
Yes, what's wrong?

358
00:19:03,590 --> 00:19:05,160
They said Mr. Ji isn't here,

359
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:06,310
so there's no one to host it.

360
00:19:06,310 --> 00:19:07,510
Who said I'm not here?

361
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:09,000
Mr. Ji.

362
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:12,230
I will inform the directors immediately.

363
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:20,480
Didn't I tell you to go home and rest?

364
00:19:20,480 --> 00:19:22,140
Why did you come to work again?

365
00:19:22,790 --> 00:19:24,220
You look exhausted.

366
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:25,720
Rui.

367
00:19:26,350 --> 00:19:27,550
I want a cup of coffee.

368
00:19:43,170 --> 00:19:45,100
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

369
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,590
Why are you looking at your phone again?

370
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:58,830
Didn't you already use my phone

371
00:19:58,830 --> 00:20:00,370
to call your mom?

372
00:20:03,510 --> 00:20:04,770
It's not to call my mom.

373
00:20:05,030 --> 00:20:06,440
I need to check the work group chats.

374
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:08,430
I haven't checked them since last night.

375
00:20:08,430 --> 00:20:09,720
I'm afraid someone is looking for me.

376
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,810
I knew it.

377
00:20:11,680 --> 00:20:13,140
Don't even think about it.

378
00:20:13,340 --> 00:20:14,850
I already asked for leave for you today.

379
00:20:14,850 --> 00:20:16,610
You are not allowed to work today.

380
00:20:16,610 --> 00:20:18,320
But the college entrance examination
isn't over yet.

381
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,380
I'm afraid that...

382
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:21,400
Without you, Purong

383
00:20:21,400 --> 00:20:23,120
will still run.

384
00:20:23,590 --> 00:20:25,880
Today, you just need to rest and recover.

385
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:27,000
No more overworking.

386
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,800
Do you hear me?

387
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:35,310
I'll put the hot water and the medicine

388
00:20:35,310 --> 00:20:36,390
here for you.

389
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:37,670
Remember to take it.

390
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:38,890
I'm leaving.

391
00:20:39,880 --> 00:20:40,970
Ride safe.

392
00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:56,390
Chef Jiao.

393
00:20:58,190 --> 00:21:00,120
This is prepared for the guests.

394
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:02,380
What guests?

395
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:04,930
Are the guests more important
or my daughter?

396
00:21:05,370 --> 00:21:06,550
When you have your own kids,

397
00:21:06,550 --> 00:21:08,540
you'll understand.

398
00:21:11,790 --> 00:21:12,400
But I...

399
00:21:21,550 --> 00:21:23,080
Chef Jiao, you can't leave.

400
00:21:23,140 --> 00:21:25,000
Dinner hasn't been prepared yet.

401
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,240
Didn't you keep asking me

402
00:21:27,240 --> 00:21:29,440
when you could try your hand at it?

403
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:31,590
Yes.

404
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:32,350
When?

405
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:33,510
Right now.

406
00:21:39,350 --> 00:21:41,480
Chef Jiao! Chef Jiao!

407
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:44,000
This young man.

408
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:47,450
Thinking he can stop me.

409
00:21:48,510 --> 00:21:49,920
-I’m sorry.
-I’m sorry.

410
00:21:50,720 --> 00:21:51,440
Mr. Tan.

411
00:21:51,440 --> 00:21:52,270
Mrs. Xu.

412
00:21:52,290 --> 00:21:53,030
Sorry.

413
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:54,700
Did the oil get on you?

414
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:55,440
No, no.

415
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:55,920
Really.

416
00:21:55,920 --> 00:21:56,920
How about you give me your clothes

417
00:21:56,920 --> 00:21:58,030
and I'll dry-clean them for you?

418
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,230
I'll have my daughter

419
00:21:59,240 --> 00:22:01,640
-bring them to your room later.
-It's okay.

420
00:22:02,020 --> 00:22:04,090
By the way, how is Miyu doing?

421
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:06,650
I heard she's sick.

422
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,470
Yes, yes.

423
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:10,530
You see, I'm bringing her food.

424
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:11,680
Is it serious?

425
00:22:13,810 --> 00:22:15,000
How should I put it?

426
00:22:15,550 --> 00:22:17,280
It's on and off.

427
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:19,070
I'm so worried.

428
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:22,530
Why don't you come with me to see her?

429
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:24,240
If Miyu knows you're visiting her,

430
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:25,340
she will be very happy.

431
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:27,860
Then she'll recover once she's happy.

432
00:22:28,070 --> 00:22:28,680
Well...

433
00:22:29,070 --> 00:22:29,790
Is that okay?

434
00:22:29,790 --> 00:22:30,730
Yes, it is.

435
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:31,600
Of course.

436
00:22:31,960 --> 00:22:32,270
Xia,

437
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:32,910
come here.

438
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,940
Could you take it to storage?

439
00:22:34,970 --> 00:22:36,400
-It’s Mr. Tan's.
-Please take it to storage for me.

440
00:22:36,400 --> 00:22:37,460
-Okay.
-Thank you.

441
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,160
I'll take you there.

442
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:38,960
Okay.

443
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:39,400
Let's go together.

444
00:22:39,400 --> 00:22:40,310
I got this.

445
00:22:40,310 --> 00:22:40,640
You take it.

446
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,240
I got this.

447
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:54,780
Miyu.

448
00:22:54,980 --> 00:22:56,110
I'm baking cookies.

449
00:22:56,270 --> 00:22:57,470
They'll be done soon.

450
00:23:00,680 --> 00:23:02,600
Go clean up.

451
00:23:03,520 --> 00:23:04,520
I just cleaned up.

452
00:23:04,530 --> 00:23:06,650
I mean you.

453
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,030
Look at what you're wearing.

454
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:09,030
Even a sack

455
00:23:09,050 --> 00:23:10,400
looks better than that.

456
00:23:10,510 --> 00:23:11,530
Go change your clothes.

457
00:23:11,530 --> 00:23:12,640
Change into that Chanel-style outfit.

458
00:23:12,640 --> 00:23:13,860
Go, go.

459
00:23:13,890 --> 00:23:15,110
Why?

460
00:23:15,400 --> 00:23:17,200
You have a visitor.

461
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:18,830
A visitor? Who?

462
00:23:18,910 --> 00:23:19,970
Miyu, it's me.

463
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,230
May I come in?

464
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:23,610
Mr. Tan is here to see you.

465
00:23:23,770 --> 00:23:25,810
He's such a gentleman.

466
00:23:25,870 --> 00:23:26,920
When he arrived at the door,

467
00:23:26,920 --> 00:23:28,980
he insisted I come in and let you know.

468
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,600
He knows his boundaries.

469
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:32,140
Where are yours?

470
00:23:32,170 --> 00:23:32,590
I...

471
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:34,690
I'll talk to you about this later.

472
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,850
Put on some lipstick.

473
00:23:38,330 --> 00:23:39,090
Enough.

474
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:44,070
Mr. Tan, please come in.

475
00:23:44,660 --> 00:23:45,990
Are you feeling better?

476
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:47,770
Much better, thank you.

477
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:48,770
Is it okay?

478
00:23:48,770 --> 00:23:50,230
Yes, come in.

479
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,030
Well,

480
00:23:52,560 --> 00:23:53,930
the hotel wants me back.

481
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,110
Well,

482
00:23:55,140 --> 00:23:56,620
isn't there

483
00:23:56,650 --> 00:23:57,950
a performance tonight?

484
00:23:57,950 --> 00:23:59,090
I'm leaving now.

485
00:23:59,110 --> 00:24:00,630
Take your time.

486
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,030
Okay.

487
00:24:01,030 --> 00:24:01,680
You two take your time talking.

488
00:24:01,680 --> 00:24:02,290
Careful, slow down.

489
00:24:02,290 --> 00:24:02,680
Okay.

490
00:24:03,440 --> 00:24:04,290
I am heading back now.

491
00:24:04,290 --> 00:24:06,020
Take your time, take your time.

492
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:07,350
Mom.

493
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:17,970
Mr. Tan, please have a seat.

494
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:19,590
Okay.

495
00:24:32,790 --> 00:24:33,460
Chef Jiao,

496
00:24:33,980 --> 00:24:35,240
why are you back again?

497
00:24:36,300 --> 00:24:37,440
Your hedgehog

498
00:24:38,590 --> 00:24:40,640
looks like a mouse.

499
00:24:41,450 --> 00:24:43,050
You didn't use enough flour.

500
00:24:43,270 --> 00:24:44,070
Let me tell you,

501
00:24:44,070 --> 00:24:45,260
you won't be able
to cut out the spines later.

502
00:24:45,260 --> 00:24:46,660
Here, watch me.

503
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:48,160
You kids.

504
00:24:48,160 --> 00:24:49,890
You really can't do without me.

505
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:51,370
Look.

506
00:24:52,310 --> 00:24:53,770
Isn't this Miyu's dinner?

507
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,160
Come on, look.

508
00:25:10,890 --> 00:25:12,750
You stayed at the airport all day?

509
00:25:14,110 --> 00:25:14,900
It's thunderstorm season.

510
00:25:14,900 --> 00:25:16,430
Many flights are grounded.

511
00:25:16,680 --> 00:25:18,080
It's okay. I'm used to it.

512
00:25:18,490 --> 00:25:20,350
Then you must not have eaten well.

513
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,880
The noodles will be ready soon.

514
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:22,680
Okay, no rush.

515
00:25:23,920 --> 00:25:25,310
Have some cookies first.

516
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:25,880
Okay.

517
00:25:31,680 --> 00:25:32,510
Okay, I got it.

518
00:25:32,530 --> 00:25:33,950
I'll come back soon.

519
00:25:34,880 --> 00:25:35,480
Tomorrow?

520
00:25:35,690 --> 00:25:37,940
I'm not sure. I can't promise.

521
00:25:40,670 --> 00:25:41,750
Okay, bye.

522
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:48,060
-Here.
-Thank you.

523
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:50,940
You must be busy with work.

524
00:25:50,940 --> 00:25:51,490
No.

525
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:58,720
You've been to the Getty Museum too?

526
00:25:58,720 --> 00:25:59,270
Yeah.

527
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:01,430
The Getty Center or the Getty Villa?

528
00:26:01,430 --> 00:26:02,430
The Getty Center.

529
00:26:02,880 --> 00:26:04,830
I just wanted to see for myself

530
00:26:04,830 --> 00:26:07,260
how amazing those masterpieces

531
00:26:07,680 --> 00:26:09,940
you usually only see in books really are.

532
00:26:10,270 --> 00:26:11,310
Then...

533
00:26:11,310 --> 00:26:12,110
How was it?

534
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:14,350
I was actually blown away

535
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:15,680
by Paul Getty's wealth.

536
00:26:16,590 --> 00:26:18,520
Degas' dancers,

537
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:19,930
Van Gogh's Irises,

538
00:26:20,070 --> 00:26:21,030
Munch's The Scream,

539
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,030
Monet's Water Lilies,

540
00:26:22,030 --> 00:26:23,270
and those portraits of Louis XIV

541
00:26:23,270 --> 00:26:24,960
covered in gold and silver,

542
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,590
all effortlessly embraced

543
00:26:26,590 --> 00:26:28,070
by this museum.

544
00:26:28,790 --> 00:26:31,510
Inside lies an elegant,
understated world of art.

545
00:26:31,510 --> 00:26:34,960
Outside unfolds a tropical, ocean breeze
filled with birdsong and blooming flowers.

546
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,920
It's simply the heaven I imagined.

547
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:42,590
I'm sorry.

548
00:26:43,110 --> 00:26:44,680
I got a bit carried away
in front of an expert.

549
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:45,640
No. No.

550
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:47,180
What you said
is exactly what I was thinking.

551
00:26:47,180 --> 00:26:48,450
I was just surprised

552
00:26:48,470 --> 00:26:50,550
at how much you know about Western art.

553
00:26:50,550 --> 00:26:51,920
Not that much.

554
00:26:52,070 --> 00:26:53,830
When I was in college,

555
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:55,160
I thought I might work

556
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:57,030
in a hotel-related
profession in the future

557
00:26:57,030 --> 00:26:58,200
and might need this knowledge.

558
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:00,440
So I read some books on art,

559
00:27:00,440 --> 00:27:02,200
and the more I read,
the more fascinated I became.

560
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,440
I just liked it,

561
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:05,730
so I learned a bit about it.

562
00:27:06,160 --> 00:27:07,750
That's not just a bit.

563
00:27:10,160 --> 00:27:10,790
The pot.

564
00:27:10,890 --> 00:27:12,820
It's okay, let me do it. Have a seat.

565
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,270
Thanks.

566
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,020
Smells so good.

567
00:28:02,090 --> 00:28:02,800
Your phone.

568
00:28:05,400 --> 00:28:06,500
It's not important.

569
00:28:06,500 --> 00:28:08,950
You skipped work to come here, didn't you?

570
00:28:12,160 --> 00:28:13,480
I know you must be worried

571
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:15,510
about the old Mr. Tan's health, right?

572
00:28:15,510 --> 00:28:17,660
He has been experiencing
chest tightness lately,

573
00:28:17,660 --> 00:28:19,260
but everything else is fine.

574
00:28:19,350 --> 00:28:20,110
Don't worry.

575
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:21,750
Even though I left the HSKP Department,

576
00:28:21,750 --> 00:28:23,720
I'm still in touch with the girls

577
00:28:23,720 --> 00:28:25,050
on the executive floor.

578
00:28:26,070 --> 00:28:27,530
If you are really worried,

579
00:28:27,550 --> 00:28:28,880
you can add me on WeChat.

580
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:31,000
Then next time you're worried,

581
00:28:31,000 --> 00:28:32,060
you can just ask me.

582
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:32,740
Okay.

583
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:34,400
Thank you, Ms. Xu.

584
00:29:00,920 --> 00:29:03,740
[Li Qiaoqi]

585
00:29:07,050 --> 00:29:08,100
Hello, Mr. Ji.

586
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:09,940
Qiaoqi.

587
00:29:10,440 --> 00:29:11,330
Miyu, she...

588
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:12,350
Mr. Ji.

589
00:29:12,910 --> 00:29:15,310
I don't know what
happened between you two.

590
00:29:15,600 --> 00:29:16,670
But regarding Miyu,

591
00:29:16,670 --> 00:29:18,400
if she doesn't want you to know,

592
00:29:18,480 --> 00:29:19,680
I can't tell you.

593
00:29:19,920 --> 00:29:20,480
Sorry.

594
00:29:20,970 --> 00:29:22,640
Okay, I know.

595
00:29:23,090 --> 00:29:23,810
Mr. Ji,

596
00:29:24,240 --> 00:29:25,160
for last night,

597
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,960
I want to thank you on behalf of Miyu.

598
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,620
The doctor said the IV worked very well.

599
00:29:28,620 --> 00:29:30,620
She just needs to rest for a few days.

600
00:29:31,760 --> 00:29:32,360
Thank you.

601
00:29:39,770 --> 00:29:40,430
Still here?

602
00:29:42,310 --> 00:29:42,940
By the way,

603
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:45,260
there's an industry exhibition
this weekend,

604
00:29:45,260 --> 00:29:46,620
and we've been invited.

605
00:29:47,830 --> 00:29:49,090
They gave us 2 tickets.

606
00:29:49,790 --> 00:29:51,450
Should I clear your schedule?

607
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:56,550
[The 15th
Shanghai International Hospitality Expo]

608
00:30:00,000 --> 00:30:03,040
Would you rather I come with you,

609
00:30:03,070 --> 00:30:05,400
or have Ms. Xu join you?

610
00:30:08,730 --> 00:30:10,690
I'll let you know tomorrow.

611
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:12,310
Okay.

612
00:30:16,090 --> 00:30:20,110
[The 15th
Shanghai International Hospitality Expo]

613
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:25,770
You're right.

614
00:30:27,180 --> 00:30:29,710
Then do you know
about the Shanghai Biennale?

615
00:30:30,460 --> 00:30:34,270
It's at the Shanghai Museum
of Contemporary Art.

616
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:37,160
I remember their theme in 2023 was...

617
00:30:37,160 --> 00:30:38,160
"Cosmos Cinema".

618
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:42,070
At that time, they had a concept called

619
00:30:42,070 --> 00:30:44,270
"All beings are equal under the stars".

620
00:30:44,550 --> 00:30:47,110
I thought that concept
was absolutely stunning.

621
00:30:47,110 --> 00:30:48,510
You really know
Shanghai's contemporary art

622
00:30:48,510 --> 00:30:49,920
like the back of your hand.

623
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:52,520
Of course. I used to
love going to exhibitions.

624
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:55,100
Are you familiar
with the scene in Hong Kong?

625
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:55,830
Unfortunately,

626
00:30:55,830 --> 00:30:58,110
I'm always in a hurry
every time I go to Hong Kong.

627
00:30:58,110 --> 00:30:59,640
Actually, I've always wanted to visit

628
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:00,720
the M+ Museum

629
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:02,820
and the Asia Art Archive.

630
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:04,160
This weekend,

631
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:05,700
there is an exhibition at M+.

632
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:07,360
Would you like to go together?

633
00:31:08,470 --> 00:31:09,550
The round trip takes only 2 days,

634
00:31:09,550 --> 00:31:11,150
so it won't affect your work.

635
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:14,240
I have to work shifts this weekend.

636
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:18,320
Miyu, there is something

637
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:21,360
that might be a bit presumptuous to say.

638
00:31:21,920 --> 00:31:23,450
You were so happy just now,

639
00:31:23,490 --> 00:31:24,510
talking about this.

640
00:31:24,510 --> 00:31:26,570
You probably didn't even realize it.

641
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:30,390
And you were very charming, really.

642
00:31:32,110 --> 00:31:33,200
When I got here, your mom told me

643
00:31:33,200 --> 00:31:35,400
that you were in a bad mood. Is that true?

644
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:37,930
Then why not treat this trip

645
00:31:38,200 --> 00:31:39,700
as a way to clear your mind?

646
00:31:39,860 --> 00:31:40,960
Maybe after you come back,

647
00:31:40,960 --> 00:31:42,420
you'll feel differently.

648
00:31:45,960 --> 00:31:47,690
No need to answer me right away.

649
00:31:48,070 --> 00:31:48,930
Think about it.

650
00:31:50,750 --> 00:31:51,940
Thank you, Mr. Tan.

651
00:31:54,390 --> 00:31:55,930
I'll get going now.

652
00:31:57,350 --> 00:31:58,160
See you tomorrow.

653
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:59,160
See you tomorrow.

654
00:32:55,010 --> 00:32:56,610
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

655
00:32:57,630 --> 00:32:58,430
Good morning.

656
00:32:58,510 --> 00:32:59,720
Good morning, Ms. Xu.

657
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,610
Ms. Xu.

658
00:33:03,550 --> 00:33:04,270
Ms. Xu.

659
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:06,140
I heard you were sick.

660
00:33:06,140 --> 00:33:07,800
So I bought some supplements.

661
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:09,890
I didn't know you'd be at work today.

662
00:33:09,890 --> 00:33:11,290
They are still in my room.

663
00:33:11,510 --> 00:33:12,900
I'll bring them to you later.

664
00:33:12,900 --> 00:33:13,790
I'm alright.

665
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:16,000
We cannot accept gifts from guests.

666
00:33:16,180 --> 00:33:17,720
As long as Yuze's exam wasn't affected.

667
00:33:17,720 --> 00:33:18,730
The exam went smoothly.

668
00:33:18,730 --> 00:33:19,670
Thank you, Miss.

669
00:33:19,690 --> 00:33:20,510
That's great.

670
00:33:21,400 --> 00:33:23,000
Today is the last day, right?

671
00:33:23,070 --> 00:33:23,920
You should hurry.

672
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,740
Don't be late.

673
00:33:24,610 --> 00:33:29,520
[Purong Hotel]

674
00:33:24,790 --> 00:33:25,920
Okay, we'll get going now.

675
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,070
Good luck on the exam.

676
00:33:27,070 --> 00:33:28,600
Thank you, Ms. Xu. Goodbye.

677
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:29,430
Take care.

678
00:33:36,600 --> 00:33:37,800
Good morning, Mr. Ji.

679
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:38,680
Good morning.

680
00:33:40,090 --> 00:33:41,430
Are you feeling better?

681
00:33:41,460 --> 00:33:42,630
I'm fully recovered.

682
00:33:42,630 --> 00:33:43,630
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

683
00:33:46,610 --> 00:33:49,110
There is an industry expo this weekend

684
00:33:49,130 --> 00:33:51,460
at Pudong New International Expo Centre.

685
00:33:52,160 --> 00:33:53,290
Want to go together?

686
00:34:01,330 --> 00:34:02,270
Mr. Tan.

687
00:34:09,949 --> 00:34:11,550
I've got plans this weekend.

688
00:34:11,560 --> 00:34:12,560
You've got plans?

689
00:34:13,170 --> 00:34:14,170
I'm sorry, Mr. Ji.

690
00:34:14,409 --> 00:34:15,610
I'll get back to work.

691
00:34:24,110 --> 00:34:24,389
[Monday, June 9]

692
00:34:29,530 --> 00:34:31,790
[Miyu]

693
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,670
Mr. Tan, let's go together.

694
00:34:45,969 --> 00:34:46,780
Okay.

695
00:34:46,500 --> 00:34:46,860
[Tan Jizhou]

696
00:34:55,290 --> 00:34:56,550
Sometimes,

697
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,240
accepting an invitation

698
00:34:58,070 --> 00:34:59,980
♪ Life is full of ♪

699
00:34:58,270 --> 00:34:59,600
doesn't mean anything.

700
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:01,800
But rejecting someone's invitation

701
00:35:01,030 --> 00:35:03,680
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

702
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:04,290
is because you have
feelings for them.

703
00:35:05,210 --> 00:35:09,060
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

704
00:35:05,830 --> 00:35:07,130
What am I afraid of?

705
00:35:10,650 --> 00:35:12,650
♪ All those confusions ♪

706
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:16,960
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

707
00:35:17,840 --> 00:35:21,840
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

708
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:27,360
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

709
00:35:28,770 --> 00:35:30,690
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

710
00:35:32,520 --> 00:35:36,230
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

711
00:35:38,040 --> 00:35:39,840
♪ Busy and restless ♪

712
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:43,870
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

713
00:35:45,220 --> 00:35:49,280
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

714
00:35:51,160 --> 00:35:53,510
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

715
00:35:54,840 --> 00:35:56,870
♪ Don't look back ♪

716
00:35:57,840 --> 00:35:59,610
♪ I've already learned ♪

717
00:36:00,390 --> 00:36:04,220
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

718
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,580
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

719
00:36:07,380 --> 00:36:11,310
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

720
00:36:12,300 --> 00:36:15,240
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

721
00:36:15,940 --> 00:36:18,550
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

722
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:20,870
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

723
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,360
Is there a problem?

724
00:36:28,690 --> 00:36:32,490
[Hong Kong, China]

725
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:31,030
Take care.

726
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,320
Good evening, Mr. Tan.

727
00:36:35,320 --> 00:36:35,760
Hello.

728
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,160
How can I help you?

729
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,030
I booked

730
00:36:38,070 --> 00:36:39,730
an Executive 80 Sea View Room.

731
00:36:40,170 --> 00:36:40,810
Okay.

732
00:36:42,550 --> 00:36:44,340
I'll just take a standard room.

733
00:36:45,570 --> 00:36:46,570
Wait a moment.

734
00:36:47,630 --> 00:36:48,550
It's fine.

735
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:50,980
This hotel has a partnership
with our company.

736
00:36:50,980 --> 00:36:52,210
I came here on my own.

737
00:36:52,360 --> 00:36:53,620
How could I let you pay?

738
00:36:55,740 --> 00:36:56,960
Alright, it's up to you.

739
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,890
Excuse me, a standard room please.

740
00:37:00,410 --> 00:37:01,760
Your room has been booked.

741
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,760
Have a good night.

742
00:37:02,960 --> 00:37:04,020
Let's go. This way.

743
00:37:05,150 --> 00:37:05,800
By the way,

744
00:37:05,820 --> 00:37:08,440
don't forget to accept
the money I transferred for the flight.

745
00:37:08,440 --> 00:37:09,550
I dragged you to this exhibition.

746
00:37:09,550 --> 00:37:10,960
I'm already very happy
that you could come.

747
00:37:10,960 --> 00:37:12,760
Let's not talk about this, okay?

748
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:14,070
I'm the happy one.

749
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:15,400
You helped me fulfill this dream

750
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:16,930
and left me with no regrets.

751
00:37:18,230 --> 00:37:18,630
Okay.

752
00:37:19,240 --> 00:37:21,440
Then I'll pick you up
at 10:00 a.m. tomorrow.

753
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,970
Remember to eat breakfast.

754
00:37:26,190 --> 00:37:26,880
See you tomorrow.

755
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:27,880
See you tomorrow.

756
00:39:03,080 --> 00:39:07,750
[Central]

757
00:39:06,190 --> 00:39:08,650
So do you still have
any regrets after today?

758
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:09,630
Today,

759
00:39:09,670 --> 00:39:12,360
we even caught the debut
of that mysterious pearl piece

760
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:13,880
from the British royal family today.

761
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,210
We were really so lucky.

762
00:39:15,960 --> 00:39:18,670
[Hans Bookstore]

763
00:39:16,880 --> 00:39:18,320
So you like pearls.

764
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:21,150
I think pearls emit

765
00:39:21,150 --> 00:39:22,960
an elegant and pure glow.

766
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,280
Just like you.

767
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,610
Want to grab a drink?

768
00:39:42,580 --> 00:39:46,540
[Moden Alley]

769
00:39:56,210 --> 00:39:56,890
Rui.

770
00:39:57,340 --> 00:39:59,340
I asked you to invite
Xu Miyu to the exhibition,

771
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:01,270
and she ended up going to Hong Kong?

772
00:40:03,190 --> 00:40:04,460
She decided it herself.

773
00:40:04,460 --> 00:40:05,530
I had no say in it.

774
00:40:06,180 --> 00:40:08,780
Do you not want to know
why she went to Hong Kong?

775
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:12,440
Please do not tell me, alright?

776
00:40:12,590 --> 00:40:13,630
Oh, you.

777
00:40:14,190 --> 00:40:16,490
They are almost together.

778
00:40:16,930 --> 00:40:18,310
Are you going to give up?

779
00:40:19,070 --> 00:40:19,840
Rui,

780
00:40:20,600 --> 00:40:23,130
how long has it been
since you came to the Bund?

781
00:40:23,800 --> 00:40:24,630
How come there are so many

782
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:25,630
new buildings?

783
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,670
I don't think I've seen them before.
